Subject: Web Server unresponsive.
Description: Web server is unresponsive/very slow. Console shows out of memory messages and process kill messages. Restart attempts result in messages saying it is attempting to stop SQL, but it never stops. To restore server functionality, we have to force a restart via power reset. The memory errors return.
Solution_Comment__c:
Re-optimized resources + suggested increasing resources.
Customer increased resources + we re-optimized new resources.
